    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required levels at MRL 2. The six not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per ASME V&V 40 Table 4 for a Class II device at MRL 2. The CFD model is deemed sufficiently credible to identify worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions. The relative hemolysis index criterion (RH < 1) is met at all five operating points. The credibility assessment team accepts the model for its intended use.",
